500 win and a bronze in the 400m free Ledecky stands on the brink of Phelps-like greatness.\", \"from\": 1173, \"to\": 1295, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her 1,500 win\", \"from\": 1198, \"to\": 1211}, {\"ngram\": \"a bronze\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"the 400m free Ledecky\", \"from\": 1228, \"to\": 1249}, {\"ngram\": \"the brink\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1269}, {\"ngram\": \"Phelps-like greatness\", \"from\": 1273, \"to\": 1294}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One more gold medal in Paris will bring her haul from four Games to nine, matching the record for most by any woman Olympic athlete held by gymnast Larisa Latynina.\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1320, \"end\": 1325, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999763531, \"rank\": 2.366952943858795e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1445, \"end\": 1460, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Larisa Latynina\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Larisa_Latynina\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One more gold medal\", \"from\": 1297, \"to\": 1316}, {\"ngram\": \"her haul\", \"from\": 1337, \"to\": 1345}, {\"ngram\": \"four Games\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1361}, {\"ngram\": \"the record\", \"from\": 1380, \"to\": 1390}, {\"ngram\": \"any woman\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1412}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic athlete\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1428}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the 800m free and possible relays still to come, Ledecky could leave Paris officially crowned the greatest female Olympian ever.\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1596, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1537, \"end\": 1542, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resourc